{"tid":1300703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啲黑警而家都已經草木皆兵","createTime":"2019-07-09T12:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:42:27.000Z","uid":274879,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8cea793c4deaaf1854f89f81cc3a25caf6fccea1","tid":1300703,"uid":274879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"而家一星期一兩次野餐行街已經<span style=\"color: red;\">做死班黑警</span>喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋大壓力到<span style=\"color: red;\">連途人記者都唔放在眼內</span><br />\n仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">每次野餐行街之後都要樹一次敵</span><br />\n佢哋應該就來崩潰架啦喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以其實暫時可以<span style=\"color: violet;\">keep住咁樣一星期行一次街野餐先</span><br />\n總之黑警退我哋就進, 好似啱啱星期日咁<br />\n黑警進我哋就散, 不受傷不被捕<br />\n等佢<span style=\"color: orange;\">壓力大到係咁搞埋啲途人同記者, 係咁樹敵</span>, 直到佢哋<span style=\"color: orange;\">徹低崩潰</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然林鄭老母先係真正對手, 但鬼叫黑警收錢做嘢, 咪睇吓老母攬佢哋幾耐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137cb864ce3af7cb53e43b7f6acabcd558af32f1","tid":1300703,"uid":82640,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"其實今日喺餐廳食飯見到有堆師奶大大聲屌差佬<br />\n其他台都慢慢自己圍內都各自各日屌埋一份<br />\n講真如果間餐廳有人係差佬<br />\n佢會谷到幾勁真係難以想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e7efdf7cccd80f3af97dfd32b0ed392d5a199a","tid":1300703,"uid":274879,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:30:25.000Z","msg":"總之搞到啲黑警係咁辣著唔關事嘅人就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啲議員成日出來好似幫手但又幫唔到咩手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過今次都好, 啲議員都係黑警敵人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789f12df9a38f07b83073f39893b7f579a988070","tid":1300703,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:33: